---
title: Slow-Cooked Pork Meatball & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Herbs
description: Our Slow Cook recipes are perfect for those cold nights - switch on your oven and get ready to cook low and slow to pack maximum flavour. We love a little ball of deliciousness and a meatball fits this description perfectly. Slow-cooked pork with a hint of our chicken
stock is rolled up nice and tight, stirred through an aromatic Indian-style curry and served with pillowy garlic rice.

